text: We all end up in the same void.
Spite is a renewable energy source.
Control is an illusion; I embraced it.
Nothing matters, so this felt right.
Just practicing for the heat death.
One less paradox to worry about.
I liked the symmetry of the outcome.
Because chaos deserves a seat at the table.
Suffering is inevitable; variety is optional.
Fate spun the wheel; I obeyed.
I flipped a coin in my head.
The end is certain, the path isn't.
Entropy wins, might as well help it.
